# 🏦 Bank Management System (Java + Swing + MySQL)

## 📌 Project Description
This is a **Bank Management System** desktop application built using **Java Swing** and **MySQL**.
It simulates basic ATM functionalities like account creation, login, deposit, withdrawal, and more.

---

## 🚀 Features
- 🔐 User Login System
- 📝 Account Registration (3-step signup)
- 💰 Deposit Money
- 💸 Withdraw Money
- ⚡ Fast Cash
- 📄 Mini Statement
- 🔄 PIN Change
- 💳 Balance Enquiry

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Java (Core Java + Swing)
- MySQL Database
- JDBC (MySQL Connector)

